nchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central" font-family="system-ui, -apple-system, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, sans-serif" font-size="14" fill="currentColor"><tspan x="288" dy="0"><tspan>Done</tspan></tspan></text><path d="M 288 108 L 288 188" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)" /><path d="M 253 278 L 253 318 L 153 318 L 153 358" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)" /><text x="203" y="318" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central" font-family="system-ui, -apple-system, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, sans-serif" font-size="14" fill="currentColor" paint-order="stroke" stroke-width="4" stroke-linejoin="round" style="stroke: var(--doodles-label-halo, transparent)"><tspan x="203" dy="0"><tspan>yes</tspan></tspan></text><path d="M 323 278 L 323 318 L 423 318 L 423 358" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)" /><text x="373" y="318" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central" font-family="system-ui, -apple-system, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, sans-serif" font-size="14" fill="currentColor" paint-order="stroke" stroke-width="4" stroke-linejoin="round" style="stroke: var(--doodles-label-halo, transparent)"><tspan x="373" dy="0"><tspan>no</tspan></tspan></text><path d="M 153 418 L 153 458 L 253 458 L 253 498" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)" /><path d="M 423 418 L 423 458 L 323 458 L 323 498" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)" /></svg>"`;
